 waypoint also supports its customers with saleleaseback transactions on existing helicopter fleets about waypoint leasing ireland limited waypoint is a global helicopter lessor providing aircraft and financing solutions to helicopter operators around the world headquartered in limerick ireland and with operations in darien ct waypoint partners with helicopter operators across a wide range of sectors including oil and gas emergency medical service search and rescue firefighting and governmental support  further information is available at httpwwwwaypointleasingcom about chc helicopter chc is a commercial operator of helicopters focused on enabling customers to go further do more and come home safely  chc provides helicopter flight services to oil and gas companies and government searchandrescue agencies and helicopter maintenance repair and overhaul services to organizations through the helione segment  the company is headquartered in vancouver and operates more than  aircraft in about  countries around the world recent news paris air show new lease of life for the h waypoint delivers s and sc helicopters to omni in brazil waypoint leasing enters chinese market view all news   learn more contact us request information sign up for press releases download our brochure high salaries push chc’s loss to €m  irish examiner epaper apps postal delivery photos competitions newspaper archive advertise with us shop death notices find a home job irishexaminer home»business high salaries push chc’s loss to €m friday march  by gordon deegan average salaries of € each for the  staff at the firm operating the €m state contract to provide helicopter search and rescue sar services contributed to losses at the firm increasing by  to €m last year chc ireland ltd provides the sar service from its four main bases at dublin sligo shannon and waterford for the state and commenced a year €m contract with the government in  the air corps withdrew from limited sar duties in  and the current c